		<title>15FOUR MARKS POETRY:SPRING DAY</title>
		<content> THE FIRST  Fields and fields covered  
 DAYS OF       in flowers              
 SPRING     Opening up to Spring       
            The drowsy door mouse      
               wakens to a sky of sun  
            After his long winter sleep
                                       
            The lush green grass       
               waiting to be used by   
            Screaming shouting children
            Buds bursting into blossom 
              showering the grass with 
            colourful petals.          
            Bouncing baby bunnies      
              bounding towards their   
            Warren.                    
                                       
           Mad March hares chasing each
              other round flower filled
           fields.                     
                                       
                                       </content>
